metadata.name: PINBALLER: Issue #2
metadata.description:
# PINBALLER Comic Issue #2

The continuing adventures of Pinballer and Voola!

Now including our first two Launchpad stories: Nullable and Peppermint, for an even bigger and more expansive read!

## Launchpad Stories

Launchpad Stories are genesis stories for community owned IP. If the community votes for your character, they’ll appear in a future issue of Pinballer, and you’ll have launched your IP to a wider audience!

We look forward to your submissions.
